data.description: Welcome to your new sanctuary, where timeless elegance and contemporary luxury converge in this meticulously upgraded 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence spanning 2,076 square feet. From the inviting guest bathroom with modern fixtures to the opulent, enduring flooring throughout, every detail has been thoughtfully considered. The open concept design seamlessly connects the living room and dining area, fostering togetherness, while the culinary masterpiece of a kitchen boasts an efficient and stylish electrical chimney. Your backyard offers a peaceful outdoor oasis, perfect for relaxation or customization to your preferences. Inside, three comfortable bedrooms provide ample space, complemented by two well-appointed bathrooms. A new fence ensures privacy and security, while fresh paint ties it all together, creating a cohesive and inviting space.
